              <div>
                <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-2 text-text-primary">After Cmd/Ctrl + B (Normalizes structure)</h4>
                <div class="bg-bg-surface border border-border-light rounded-md p-3 font-mono text-sm">
                  <div class="text-text-secondary">HTML:</div>
                  <div class="text-text-primary mt-1">&lt;p&gt;He<span class="bg-yellow-200 dark:bg-yellow-900/40 font-bold">&lt;strong&gt;llo wo&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;rld&lt;/strong&gt;</span>&lt;/p&gt;</div>
